title: Terrace at the Village..First Floor Gorgeous Newly Remodeled 1 Bedroom
posting_body: ['Relocating or looking for a the perfect place to live?', 'Reserve a gorgeous newly remodeled one bedroom one bath apartment home today!', 'Terrace at the Village is a luxury apartment complex that has everything you are looking for.', 'Unit benefits brand new laminate flooring throughout the entire apartment, crown and base molding, spacious kitchen with small dining area, white quartz kitchen counter and bar, gas stove, dishwasher, built in microwave and plenty of closet space.', 'The complex is located in an upscale neighborhood of the Valley Village area, entire building was remodeled five years ago, it has a large sparkling swimming pool, new fitness center, gated parking, intercom entry system, community barbecue grills and 24 hour laundry facility with new machines.', 'We are a short distance from the famous Chandler Bike path where you can go and submerse yourself in the interesting and intricate art that lines the path.', 'We are conveniently located steps away from the Orange Line, North Hollywood Metro station, and 101 & 170 freeways.', 'Close to Gelsons, Ralphs, Walgreens, less that 2 miles away from Universal City Walk shopping and dining.', 'To view a virtual tour of unit similar to 119 - 1Bed/1Bath - <URL>', '-Quoted security deposit is on approved credit.', '-6 or 12 month lease - Six month lease available with $200 surcharge.', 'The rent, deposit, concession and terms listed in this ad are only valid for the actual date that this ad was initially posted.']
